beer.beer_description:
I 1859 ble Frydenlund bryggeri grunnlagt på løkka Frydenlund i Oslo av skipskaptein Mads Langaard. 

Frydenlund Belgisk Hveteøl er brygget etter ølstilen Wit med både bygg- og hvetemalt, krydret med sitrusskall og koriander. Dette hveteølet er ufiltrert og har derfor en uklar strågul farge, og en frisk smak med preg av appelsin, koriander og nellik. 

Frydenlund Belgisk Hveteøl passer fint i følge med fiskeretter, skalldyr, kylling og krydret mat. Serveringstemperatur: 3 - 6 °C.

items.badge_description: Happy Untappd anniversary to you! Thanks for sticking around and drinking socially with us. Cheers! That's 9 years on Untappd!

Even the vikings had to take a break from marauding once in a while. We like to think that, like us, they enjoy relaxing with a brew from their homeland. That's 250 different beers from a brewery from Norway. Try 5 more for Level 51!

items.badge_description: Thanks for staying at home, and checking in with Untappd! It allows us to stay connected to a community of beer lovers, just like you, even if we can't be in the same physical location. From our home to yours, cheers and stay safe!

While spontaneity can be fun, sometimes you want to make sure your adventure will rock. Checkout the menu at an Untappd Verified Venue before visiting and know exactly what’s on tap! That's 50 check-ins at venue that is verified. Try 5 more for Level 11!

Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 95 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower. Try 5 more for Level 20!
